subject: Re: [junit] Problem in the test suite
msgSnippet: ... This is not how to use JUnitPerf s TimedTest. Please go to the JUnitPerf site (search through Google) and read the tutorial. This test code does nothing
messageBody:
Harbir wrote:

> public void testClaimsBrowserStatusofone(){
> long maxTimeexpected=2500;
>
> Test test1=new MyWebtest("testClaimsBrowseByStatusup");
> Test test11=new TimedTest(test1,maxTimeexpected);
> }

This is not how to use JUnitPerf's TimedTest. Please go to the JUnitPerf
site (search through Google) and read the tutorial. This test code does
nothing and the failure you see is meaningless. Try again from scratch.

Good luck.
